Script
    Purpose
fetch_odds.py
    Connects to an external API and grabs upcoming sports betting odds.
fetch_news.py
    Fetches the latest sports-related news articles.
fetch_supabase.py
    Pulls historical game/match data from your Supabase database.
merge_data.py
    Merges the three datasets into one object.
summarize.py
    Sends the merged data to OpenAI and gets a summarized version for Discord users.
config.py
    Loads API keys and settings from your .env file for secure access.
